STATE of North Carolina
v.
Chauncey MARSHBURN. No. 175P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 24, 2004. Chauncey Marshburn, Pro Se. Joan M. Cunningham, Assistant Attorney General, G. Dewey Hudson, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 6th day of April 2004 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 24th day of June 2004."
Justice WAINWRIGHT recused.
